events.name: CodeCamp 2023
events.detail: Join us for a weekend of coding challenges, workshops, and networking with fellow developers. Explore the latest technologies and enhance your coding skills.

events.name: DevFest XYZ
events.detail: DevFest XYZ is a celebration of developers and technology enthusiasts. Dive into hands-on sessions, learn from industry experts, and connect with like-minded individuals.

events.name: Hackathon Expo
events.detail: Calling all hackers and innovators! Participate in our 24-hour hackathon and showcase your projects at the Hackathon Expo. Exciting prizes and opportunities await.

events.name: Web Summit 2023
events.detail: Web Summit is the largest technology conference in the world. Join thousands of developers, entrepreneurs, and industry leaders for insightful talks, workshops, and networking.

events.name: AI Bootcamp 2023
events.detail: Explore the latest advancements in artificial intelligence at AI Bootcamp 2023. Engage in hands-on workshops, attend expert-led sessions, and discover the future of AI.

events.name: Mobile App Summit
events.detail: Join us for the Mobile App Summit and dive into the world of mobile development. Learn about the latest trends, tools, and best practices in creating successful mobile applications.

events.name: Blockchain Hackathon
events.detail: Calling all blockchain enthusiasts! Participate in our Blockchain Hackathon and showcase your decentralized solutions. Network with industry experts and win exciting prizes.

events.name: DevOps Conference
events.detail: Learn about the latest trends in DevOps at our annual DevOps Conference. Gain insights from experienced practitioners, participate in hands-on labs, and optimize your development workflow.

events.name: Game Developers Expo
events.detail: Immerse yourself in the world of game development at the Game Developers Expo. Discover new tools, techniques, and industry trends. Connect with fellow game developers and designers.

events.name: Frontend  Bootcamp
events.detail: Stay ahead in frontend development! Join us at the Frontend Frameworks Summit to explore the latest frameworks, libraries, and best practices for building modern web applications.

events.name: Cloud Computing Forum
events.detail: Unlock the power of the cloud at the Cloud Computing Forum. Learn from cloud experts, explore cutting-edge technologies, and discover how cloud computing is transforming industries.

events.name: Python Developers Retreat
events.detail: Escape to the Python Developers Retreat for an immersive experience in Python programming. Connect with Python enthusiasts, engage in coding challenges, and enhance your Python skills.

events.name: UX/UI Design Bootcamp
events.detail: Elevate your design skills at the UX/UI Design Bootcamp. Dive into user experience and user interface design principles, participate in hands-on projects, and create delightful user interfaces.

events.name: Tech Innovation Hack
events.detail: Experience the future at the Tech Innovation Summit. Explore groundbreaking technologies, hear from industry visionaries, and gain insights into the next wave of technological innovation.
